tell us what you do,

00:19:56.770 --> 00:19:58.635
and also if you
have a sacred space.

00:19:58.635 --> 00:19:59.260
AUDIENCE: Sure.

00:19:59.260 --> 00:20:00.950
OK.

00:20:00.950 --> 00:20:01.840
