00:23:56.410 --> 00:23:59.320
Hashtag how I thrive.

00:23:59.320 --> 00:24:01.760
The reason for that
is that I really

00:24:01.760 --> 00:24:04.790
believe that we can
get to the point

00:24:04.790 --> 00:24:08.385
where we can prevent a lot of
people having their own wake

00:24:08.385 --> 00:24:09.200
up calls.

00:24:09.200 --> 00:24:11.240
We can learn from each
other's wake up calls.

00:24:11.240 --> 00:24:14.010
Why can't you learn from
mine, or Hilary Clinton's?

00:24:14.010 --> 00:24:16.100
Why do have to have your own?

00:24:16.100 --> 00:24:21.300
And also we can learn from
your story about the ballet.

00:24:21.300 --> 00:24:26.930
Or learn from your sacred
space, and get ideas

00:24:26.930 --> 00:24:29.380
about what can help us thrive.

00:24:29.380 --> 00:24:31.280
And to make it super
easy, I'm going

00:24:31.280 --> 00:24:33.890
to give you my
email address so you

00:24:33.890 --> 00:24:37.600
can bypass the Huffington
Post bureaucracy.

00:24:37.600 --> 00:24:42.600
Arianna-- with one R and
two N's @huffingtonpost.com.

00:24:42.600 --> 00:24:44.800
One of the good things
about founding a company

00:24:44.800 --> 00:24:46.480
is that you get the
good email address.

