00:33:32.780 --> 00:33:36.237
that you do to seek out well
being and those quiet spaces

00:33:36.237 --> 00:33:38.570
in your life where you can
reflect and be more creative?

00:33:38.570 --> 00:33:42.530
Or are you actively seeking
out people, places, things

00:33:42.530 --> 00:33:45.547
that will drive more wisdom
into your life in general?

00:33:45.547 --> 00:33:46.630
ARIANNA HUFFINGTON: Great.

00:33:46.630 --> 00:33:49.230
First of all on the
alarm clock, you know,

00:33:49.230 --> 00:33:52.935
Pottery Barn has some great
vintage-looking alarm clocks.

00:33:56.130 --> 00:33:57.990
