brains, and has seen

00:36:06.790 --> 00:36:10.540
incredible amounts
of delta waves

00:36:10.540 --> 00:36:13.400
that have to do with
creativity, happiness.

00:36:13.400 --> 00:36:17.020
So again, we have
a lot of data that

00:36:17.020 --> 00:36:21.137
can help validate a
certain way of living.

