00:37:04.700 --> 00:37:05.700
ARIANNA HUFFINGTON: Yes.

00:37:05.700 --> 00:37:07.860
First of all, my
youngest daughter--

00:37:07.860 --> 00:37:09.970
I have two
daughters-- 23 and 25.

00:37:09.970 --> 00:37:13.150
