change, partner with somebody.

00:38:50.200 --> 00:38:52.990
And then it's easier
to support each other,

00:38:52.990 --> 00:38:54.940
to celebrate when
you're doing it,

00:38:54.940 --> 00:38:58.780
and to not judge yourselves,
but help each other

00:38:58.780 --> 00:39:00.285
when you backtrack.

